WEBVTT

00:00.634 --> 00:03.637
[ DRAMATIC MUSIC PLAYS ]

00:34.935 --> 00:37.238
[ DOG BARKING ]

00:38.706 --> 00:40.474
STOP!

00:45.479 --> 00:48.182
[ GRUNTS ]

00:48.182 --> 00:49.750
[ BOTH GRUNTING ]

00:52.620 --> 00:53.654
LET GO OF ME!

00:55.556 --> 00:57.591
BEING A COP IN LOS ANGELES

00:57.591 --> 01:00.894
IS DIFFERENT FROM PATROLLING
OTHER CITIES.

01:00.894 --> 01:02.930
NOT EVERY OFFICER
CAN TAKE THE HEAT.

01:02.930 --> 01:05.199
[ SIREN WAILING ]

01:20.914 --> 01:22.250
[ TIRES SCREECH ]

01:22.250 --> 01:23.684
[ WAILING STOPS ]

01:27.087 --> 01:29.223
[ SIGHS ]

01:29.223 --> 01:33.294
IT'LL BE YOU AGAIN.
IT AIN'T GONNA BE ME.

01:33.294 --> 01:35.729
SO, MENDOZA WAS HOME
WATERING HIS LAWN

01:35.729 --> 01:39.533
WHEN TWO THUGS ROLLED UP
AND BURIED ONE IN HIS SHOULDER.

01:41.869 --> 01:45.239
HEY.
LOOK AT THESE GUYS.

01:45.239 --> 01:46.707
I AM READY
FOR MY SPONGE BATH.

01:46.707 --> 01:49.076
YEAH, I JUST NEED YOU TO TURN
YOUR HEAD AND COUGH FIRST.

01:49.076 --> 01:51.245
[ LAUGHS, GROANS ]

01:51.245 --> 01:52.246
ASSHOLE.

01:52.246 --> 01:53.981
YOU OKAY, BROTHER?

01:53.981 --> 01:55.416
YEAH, I'M SORE,
BUT FINE.

01:55.416 --> 01:57.918
VICTORIA, THE KIDS?
SCARED.

01:57.918 --> 02:00.321
THOSE GANGSTERS HAD SOME BALLS
COMING UP IN MY HOOD.

02:00.321 --> 02:02.390
GAME'S CHANGING.

02:02.390 --> 02:06.527
WHAT IF THEY GOT A GREEN LIGHT
OUT ON ME?

02:06.527 --> 02:07.561
MY FAMILY...

02:07.561 --> 02:09.530
[ CLEARS THROAT ]
EXCUSE ME, OFFICERS.

02:09.530 --> 02:11.265
I NEED YOU TO WRAP THIS UP.

02:11.265 --> 02:14.435
COUNCILMAN CRAIG IS HERE WITH
A PHOTOGRAPHER FROM THE TIMES.

02:14.435 --> 02:15.836
COUNCILMAN CAN WAIT.

02:15.836 --> 02:17.238
WE'RE ON A TIGHT SCHEDULE.

02:17.238 --> 02:18.672
HE'S NOT YOUR PHOTO-OP.

02:18.672 --> 02:20.241
YOU CAN SAVE THE P.R. STUNT
FOR SOMEBODY ELSE.

02:20.241 --> 02:21.642
HEY, HEY, HEY, HEY.
LOOK.

02:21.642 --> 02:23.143
GIVEN THE COUNCILMAN'S
TOUGH STANCE ON CRIME,

02:23.143 --> 02:25.579
I KNOW HE'S ANXIOUS TO SPEAK
WITH OFFICER MENDOZA,

02:25.579 --> 02:27.215
THANK HIM
FOR ALL THAT HE'S DONE,

02:27.215 --> 02:29.016
BUT THAT'S ONE OF OUR GUYS
LYING THERE.

02:29.016 --> 02:32.353
AND, UH, WE NEED A FEW MORE
MINUTES WITH HIM.

02:32.353 --> 02:35.756
I'LL LET YOU KNOW
WHEN WE'RE DONE.

02:35.756 --> 02:37.491
[ CLEARS THROAT ]

02:41.429 --> 02:44.164
[ BABY CRYING ]

02:44.164 --> 02:46.767
[ EXHALING SHARPLY ]

02:46.767 --> 02:49.270
[ CHUCKLES ]

02:49.270 --> 02:51.038
I'LL BE RIGHT THERE, MA.

02:51.038 --> 02:52.873
SUDDEN BURST OF ENERGY?

02:52.873 --> 02:54.041
YEAH.

02:54.041 --> 02:57.311
THE BABY SLEPT FOR FOUR HOURS
LAST NIGHT.

02:57.311 --> 03:00.648
OH,
I'M GLAD YOU GOT SOME REST.

03:00.648 --> 03:03.317
I FEEL LIKE A NEW PERSON.

03:03.317 --> 03:06.053
YOU KNOW,
YOU'RE GONNA DRY UP YOUR MILK

03:06.053 --> 03:09.457
IF YOU KEEP UP ALL
THAT EXERCISING AND DIETING.

03:09.457 --> 03:11.259
[ CELLPHONE CHIMES ]

03:11.259 --> 03:13.561
AREN'T YOU GONNA GET THAT?

03:13.561 --> 03:17.064
[ BREATHES DEEPLY ]

03:17.064 --> 03:18.766
[ SIGHS ]

03:18.766 --> 03:20.334
HOMICIDE IN THE HILLS.

03:20.334 --> 03:22.470
GOOD NEWS IS THAT COPPER
FROM ALVARADO DIVISION

03:22.470 --> 03:24.204
WHO GOT SHOT
IN FRONT OF HIS HOUSE

03:24.204 --> 03:25.706
IS GONNA MAKE A FULL RECOVERY.

03:25.706 --> 03:28.609
THE BAD NEWS IS THESE ASSHOLES
KNOW WHERE HE LIVES.

03:28.609 --> 03:31.445
AND F.Y.I. -- MENDOZA'S
IN PRETTY GOOD SPIRITS.

03:31.445 --> 03:33.814
HE'S JUST HAPPY HE GOT SHOT
IN HIS LEFT SHOULDER

03:33.814 --> 03:34.782
AND NOT HIS RIGHT.

03:34.782 --> 03:36.183
IT WON'T AFFECT
HIS JUMP SHOT!

03:36.183 --> 03:37.385
[ LAUGHTER ]

03:37.385 --> 03:39.853
MOVING ON,
BREAK OUT YOUR SUNSCREEN.

03:39.853 --> 03:41.889
IT'S GONNA BE ANOTHER HOT ONE
HERE IN THE CITY OF ANGELS.

03:41.889 --> 03:43.824
HIGH TEMPS
LEAD TO SHORT FUSES.

03:43.824 --> 03:46.159
DOMESTICS ARE GOING
THROUGH THE ROOF.

03:46.159 --> 03:47.628
RIGHT,
PEOPLE PUNCHING EACH OTHER

03:47.628 --> 03:49.397
'CAUSE THEY'RE
HOT AND SWEATY.

03:49.397 --> 03:50.531
CLASSY.

03:50.531 --> 03:51.965
YEAH,
EXPECT POWER OUTAGES,

03:51.965 --> 03:53.901
TRAFFIC SIGNALS TO BE DOWN,
AND STAY HYDRATED.

03:53.901 --> 03:56.504
YOU PASS OUT,
YOU'RE USELESS TO ME. ALL RIGHT?

03:56.504 --> 03:58.171
NOW, BEFORE WE ROLL OUT,

03:58.171 --> 04:00.574
THESE FRESH MUFFINS
IN THE BACK HERE

04:00.574 --> 04:03.344
ARE COMPLIMENTS
OF COOPER'S GIRLFRIEND.

04:03.344 --> 04:04.378
AHH.
YEAH.

04:04.378 --> 04:05.746
NICE.
[ WHISTLES ]

04:05.746 --> 04:08.716
Dewey: SHE'S GOT
THE SWEETEST MUFFINS IN TOWN.

04:08.716 --> 04:09.883
[ LAUGHTER ]

04:09.883 --> 04:11.952
AND SHE'S WAITING FOR YOU
IN THE LOBBY, SO...

04:11.952 --> 04:14.355
ALL RIGHT, GO!
ROLL OUT! BE SAFE!

04:14.355 --> 04:15.823
GO GET HER, ROMEO!

04:15.823 --> 04:17.157
GIRLFRIEND, SIR?

04:17.157 --> 04:20.761
CONVERTING AN ON-DUTY CONTACT
INTO AN OFF-DUTY RELATIONSHIP?

04:20.761 --> 04:24.064
MY LAST F.T.O. TOLD ME
ABOUT THE THREE P's --

04:24.064 --> 04:25.599
PRIDE, POWER, AND PUSSY.

04:25.599 --> 04:27.067
THAT GONNA BE A PROBLEM
FOR YOU?

04:27.067 --> 04:28.268
NO.

04:28.268 --> 04:30.338
I'M HAPPILY MARRIED.

04:30.338 --> 04:32.940
WELL, THE ONES WITH THE WEDDING
BANDS ARE ALWAYS THE WORST ONES.

04:32.940 --> 04:34.775
[ CHUCKLES ]
I'M NOT LIKE THE OTHER GUYS.

04:34.775 --> 04:37.378
YEAH. WE'LL SEE.
YOU WAIT HERE.

04:42.983 --> 04:44.552
AMANDA?

04:44.552 --> 04:46.086
DID YOU LIKE
MY MUFFINS?

04:46.086 --> 04:48.789
HOW MANY TIMES DO WE HAVE
TO HAVE THIS CONVERSATION?

04:48.789 --> 04:51.024
YOU'VE GOT TO STOP
COMING BY THE STATION.

04:51.024 --> 04:52.426
THIS IS YOUR LAST CHANCE.

04:52.426 --> 04:54.928
I AM NOT TAKING YOU
TO THE MOVIES.

04:57.064 --> 04:58.432
IS IT MY DRESS?

04:58.432 --> 05:00.133
[ SIGHS ]

05:00.133 --> 05:02.470
NO.

05:02.470 --> 05:03.804
IT'S VERY PRETTY.

05:05.172 --> 05:08.008
AND YOU'RE A VERY LOVELY
YOUNG WOMAN.

05:08.008 --> 05:11.379
YOU'RE JUST NOT MY TYPE.

05:13.180 --> 05:15.048
IT'S YOUR LOSS.

05:23.524 --> 05:25.726
[ SIGHS, SNIFFS ]

05:25.726 --> 05:29.597
DUDE, IF YOU DON'T SMASH
THAT BISCUIT, I WILL, OKAY?

05:29.597 --> 05:31.899
GOOD LUCK WITH THAT.
SHE'S RETARDED, NOT BLIND.

05:31.899 --> 05:33.467
SEE? HE'S FUNNY.

05:33.467 --> 05:36.136
YOU GOING TO COMEDY SCHOOL, KID.
I LIKE THAT.

05:36.136 --> 05:39.440
Watters: ALL RIGHT.
GUYS AND GALS, HAVE A SEAT.

05:41.341 --> 05:42.643
LISTEN UP.

05:43.544 --> 05:44.978
I KNOW
YOU'VE ALL HEARD RUMORS

05:44.978 --> 05:47.748
THAT IT WAS THE EASTSIDE G's
THAT SHOT MENDOZA,

05:47.748 --> 05:50.484
BUT WE DO NOT KNOW YET.

05:50.484 --> 05:51.919
THE SHOOTERS
WERE WEARING HOODIES,

05:51.919 --> 05:54.021
AND ALL WE GOT IS A MAKE
AND MODEL ON THE VEHICLE.

05:54.021 --> 05:58.125
SO ALL YOU GUYS WHO ARE LOOKING
TO GIVE KIWI SHAMPOOS,

05:58.125 --> 05:59.627
CALM DOWN.

05:59.627 --> 06:02.295
AS YOU KNOW, R.H.D.
IS HANDLING THE INVESTIGATION

06:02.295 --> 06:04.598
AND HAS ASKED THAT IF YOU ARREST
ANYONE FROM THAT CLIQUE

06:04.598 --> 06:08.101
TO PASS ON COPIES
OF ALL YOUR F.I.s.

06:08.101 --> 06:10.804
GOT IT?

06:10.804 --> 06:11.972
GOT IT?

06:11.972 --> 06:13.140
All: YES, MA'AM.

06:13.140 --> 06:16.410
THANK YOU. SHERMAN,
YOU HAD SOMETHING TO SAY?

06:16.410 --> 06:17.945
Lowe: HEY, POSTER BOY.

06:17.945 --> 06:19.513
Calzano:
VILLAGE PEOPLE REUNION TOUR!
[ WHISTLES ]

06:19.513 --> 06:21.014
All:
WHOO! WHOO! WHOO! WHOO! WHOO!

06:21.014 --> 06:24.585
I'LL BE SIGNING AUTOGRAPHS
AT THE END OF WATCH.

06:24.585 --> 06:25.919
SO DREAMY.
ALL RIGHT. ENOUGH.

06:25.919 --> 06:28.656
UM, I JUST WANTED
TO LET EVERYBODY KNOW

06:28.656 --> 06:31.892
I'M ORGANIZING A BARBECUE
FUNDRAISER FOR MENDOZA,

06:31.892 --> 06:34.161
HELP HIM COVER
HIS MEDICAL BILLS.

06:34.161 --> 06:36.930
THE FLIER'S IN THE BREAK ROOM
FOR ANYBODY WHO'S INTERESTED.

06:36.930 --> 06:39.900
HE'S GONNA NEED
FULL SHOULDER REPLACEMENT.

06:39.900 --> 06:42.135
IT'S GONNA BE
A LONG RECOVERY.

06:42.135 --> 06:44.805
MENDOZA'S ALWAYS BEEN THERE
FOR US,

06:44.805 --> 06:47.007
WHETHER TO COVER A SHIFT
OR VOLUNTEER FOR O.T.

06:47.007 --> 06:51.344
I DON'T KNOW ABOUT ANYBODY ELSE,
BUT I'M GONNA DONATE MY DAYS.

06:51.344 --> 06:53.313
YOU SHOULD, TOO.

06:53.313 --> 06:54.347
THANKS.

06:54.347 --> 06:55.449
Watters: ALL RIGHT.

06:55.449 --> 06:57.785
ONLY 10:00
IN THE MORNING.

06:57.785 --> 07:00.554
IT'S ALREADY
A SAUNA OUT HERE.

07:00.554 --> 07:02.923
HOW'D YOU MEET
YOUR GIRLFRIEND?

07:02.923 --> 07:03.991
STARBUCKS.

07:03.991 --> 07:06.026
SHE SWEEPS UP,
TAKES OUT THE TRASH.

07:06.026 --> 07:08.161
SOUNDS LIKE OUR JOB.

07:08.161 --> 07:10.430
YOU'VE YET TO PROVE YOURSELF
WITH A BROOM.

07:10.430 --> 07:12.466
STARBUCKS HAS A PENSION PLAN
AND BENEFITS.

07:12.466 --> 07:13.867
MAYBE YOU SHOULD APPLY.

07:13.867 --> 07:15.569
Manager:
AND IT'S YOUR FAULT!

07:15.569 --> 07:16.804
Mr. Livermore:
IT'S NOT MY FAULT.

07:16.804 --> 07:18.472
THE GPS TOLD ME TO TURN LEFT!

07:18.472 --> 07:19.973
OH, GPS, MY ASS!

07:19.973 --> 07:21.408
YOU ALMOST RAN OVER
SOME OF MY GOLFERS

07:21.408 --> 07:22.643
BEFORE YOU CRASHED INTO --
HEY, ENOUGH!

07:22.643 --> 07:24.211
HE COULD HAVE KILLED SOMEONE!

07:24.211 --> 07:25.713
OKAY.

07:25.713 --> 07:28.048
COULD I SEE YOUR LICENSE,
SIR?

07:34.254 --> 07:36.356
MR. LIVERMORE?

07:36.356 --> 07:37.525
YES.

07:37.525 --> 07:38.992
YOUR LICENSE EXPIRED
14 MONTHS AGO.

07:38.992 --> 07:40.828
YOU PLANNING ON
GETTING IT RENEWED?

07:40.828 --> 07:45.198
WELL, I WENT A FEW TIMES.
THE LINES WERE TOO LONG.

07:45.198 --> 07:48.035
I'M GONNA HAVE TO
HANG ON TO THIS...

07:48.035 --> 07:50.738
AND WRITE YOU A CITATION FOR
DRIVING WITH AN EXPIRED LICENSE.

07:50.738 --> 07:53.507
HEY!

07:53.507 --> 07:54.708
YOU CALM DOWN.

07:54.708 --> 07:56.376
Manager:
I'M CHILLING. I'M CHILLING.

07:56.376 --> 07:59.813
UNFORTUNATELY, WE'RE ALSO GONNA
HAVE TO IMPOUND THE VEHICLE.

07:59.813 --> 08:01.715
WELL, THEN,
CAN I HAVE MY LICENSE BACK?

08:01.715 --> 08:04.585
NO, NOT TILL YOU GO TO THE DMV
AND PASS THE TEST.

08:04.585 --> 08:07.521
I WAS A P-51 MUSTANG PILOT
IN THE WAR!

08:07.521 --> 08:10.624
THE INSTRUMENTS IN MY CAR
FAILED, NOT ME.

08:10.624 --> 08:12.292
I UNDERSTAND THAT, SIR.

08:12.292 --> 08:14.427
BUT WE HAVE A PROCEDURE
WE HAVE TO FOLLOW

08:14.427 --> 08:16.797
TO MAKE SURE THAT YOU'RE CAPABLE
OF DRIVING SAFELY.

08:16.797 --> 08:18.599
I'M FINE TO DRIVE!

08:18.599 --> 08:21.702
MR. LIVERMORE.
I'M EX-ARMY, OKAY?

08:21.702 --> 08:24.672
WE APPRECIATE YOUR SERVICE.

08:24.672 --> 08:28.241
OH, UH...
PLEASE, I LIVE ALONE.

08:28.241 --> 08:31.945
HOW AM I GONNA GET MY GROCERIES
AND GO TO THE DOCTOR?

08:31.945 --> 08:34.615
HUH?

08:39.019 --> 08:40.253
STAY HERE.

08:40.253 --> 08:42.255
YEAH.

08:42.255 --> 08:45.793
YOU KNOW WHAT YOU SAID
ABOUT CATCH AND RELEASE?

08:45.793 --> 08:49.763
THIS IS A FISH
YOU THROW BACK.

08:54.902 --> 08:58.238
OKAY.
WRITE THE CITATION.

09:01.642 --> 09:03.777
HIKER FOUND THE BODY
THIS MORNING.

09:03.777 --> 09:04.912
GOT AN I.D.?

09:04.912 --> 09:06.446
FOUND A WALLET
IN THE BRUSH.

09:06.446 --> 09:09.883
I.D. SAYS IT'S RICK DAWSON,
BUT WE MIGHT HAVE TO GO DENTAL.

09:09.883 --> 09:11.251
DID YOU RUN THE NAME?

09:11.251 --> 09:14.154
HIS WIFE REPORTED HIM MISSING
THREE DAYS AGO.

09:14.154 --> 09:16.824
WITNESSES?

09:16.824 --> 09:19.660
JUST BAMBI
AND THUMPER...

09:19.660 --> 09:22.529
OOH.

09:22.529 --> 09:24.297
Ruben: MNH.

09:24.297 --> 09:25.398
WHEW.

09:25.398 --> 09:28.101
AFTER YOU.

09:32.105 --> 09:34.708
THEY TAUGHT US TO FIND WAYS
TO CONNECT WITH PEOPLE

09:34.708 --> 09:35.976
IN THE ACADEMY.

09:37.845 --> 09:39.212
THAT'S TOUCHING.

09:39.212 --> 09:40.981
YEAH, WELL, I WAS CONNECTING
WITH THAT OLD VET,

09:40.981 --> 09:42.449
AND YOU STILL
PULLED THE RUG OUT.

09:42.449 --> 09:43.917
YOU DON'T ENDANGER
PUBLIC SAFETY

09:43.917 --> 09:45.518
BECAUSE YOU HAVE A CONNECTION
WITH THE OFFENDER.

09:45.518 --> 09:46.987
NO, YOU KNOW,
I GET THE CITATION.

09:46.987 --> 09:48.321
BUT IMPOUNDING THE VEHICLE?

09:48.321 --> 09:50.090
IT'S GONNA COST HIM
AN EXTRA 150 BUCKS.

09:50.090 --> 09:51.825
THE GUY'S
PROBABLY BARELY SURVIVING

09:51.825 --> 09:53.160
OFF HIS SOCIAL SECURITY.

09:53.160 --> 09:55.528
YOU THINK I DID IT
JUST TO BE AN ASSHOLE?

09:55.528 --> 09:58.699
YES, SIR.

09:58.699 --> 10:00.868
SANTA MONICA
FARMER'S MARKET.

10:00.868 --> 10:03.771
10 DEAD, 63 INJURED
BECAUSE SOME OLD GUY

10:03.771 --> 10:06.573
MISTOOK THE ACCELERATOR
FOR THE BRAKE.

10:06.573 --> 10:08.742
NOT ON MY WATCH.

10:08.742 --> 10:11.044
[ SIGHS ] YOU'D UNDERSTAND
IF YOU'D SERVED.

10:11.044 --> 10:13.513
I TOLD YOU.
I DID A TOUR OF DUTY.

10:13.513 --> 10:15.615
BASKIN-ROBBINS.

10:17.450 --> 10:19.853
WE'RE GONNA BEAT THE HEAT.

10:19.853 --> 10:21.388
GO VISIT MY OLD COMRADES

10:21.388 --> 10:24.658
AND GET A NICE BIG-ASS SCOOP
OF PISTACHIO NUT.

10:29.797 --> 10:32.099
WHERE'S ANN DAWSON?

10:37.237 --> 10:39.740
[ FIGHTERS EXHALING SHARPLY,
GRUNTING ]

10:39.740 --> 10:41.809
ANN DAWSON?

10:44.177 --> 10:45.078
CAN I HELP YOU?

10:45.078 --> 10:47.247
DETECTIVES ADAMS
AND ROBINSON.

10:47.247 --> 10:50.250
WE NEED TO SPEAK WITH YOU
IN PRIVATE, PLEASE.

10:51.484 --> 10:55.055
HE WAS
THE LOVE OF MY LIFE.

10:55.055 --> 10:59.626
BEEN MY MANAGER
SINCE I WAS 17.

10:59.626 --> 11:02.429
THIS...

11:02.429 --> 11:04.231
THIS PLACE WAS HIS DREAM.

11:06.099 --> 11:09.837
MRS. DAWSON, I NEED TO ASK YOU
SOME QUESTIONS.

11:11.438 --> 11:16.376
IF AT ANY TIME YOU WANT TO STOP,
JUST LET ME KNOW.

11:16.376 --> 11:19.412
WHEN WAS THE LAST TIME
YOU SAW RICK?

11:19.412 --> 11:22.149
THREE DAYS AGO,
BEFORE HE LEFT FOR HIS HIKE.

11:22.149 --> 11:23.784
DID HE USUALLY GO HIKING?

11:23.784 --> 11:25.786
YEAH,
THAT WAS HIS THING.

11:25.786 --> 11:27.821
IT'S HOW
HE CLEARED HIS HEAD.

11:27.821 --> 11:32.092
HE ALWAYS GOT HOME
BEFORE IT GOT DARK, THOUGH.

11:32.092 --> 11:34.862
AND DID YOU CALL HIM
WHEN HE DIDN'T COME HOME?

11:34.862 --> 11:38.732
LOTS OF TIMES,
BUT THERE WAS NO ANSWER.

11:40.200 --> 11:43.070
I WENT TO LOOK FOR HIM
IN THE CANYON.

11:43.070 --> 11:44.805
WHAT TIME WAS THAT?

11:44.805 --> 11:47.274
UH...

11:47.274 --> 11:50.844
ABOUT 7:00?

11:50.844 --> 11:52.913
WAS RICK UPSET?

11:52.913 --> 11:55.715
ANYTHING
SEEM OFF ABOUT HIM?

11:55.715 --> 11:58.485
ACTUALLY, HE WAS GREAT.

11:58.485 --> 12:03.190
LAST THING WE TALKED ABOUT
WAS MY BIG COMEBACK MATCH.

12:05.558 --> 12:09.129
HE WAS THE ONLY ONE
THAT STILL BELIEVED IN ME.

12:11.231 --> 12:13.666
WE'RE SORRY
FOR YOUR LOSS.

12:13.666 --> 12:16.837
[ CAMERA SHUTTER CLICKING ]

12:16.837 --> 12:19.372
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

12:19.372 --> 12:23.944
NATE TOLD ME TO TAKE HIS TOY
TO WORK TO GET THE BAD GUYS.

12:23.944 --> 12:26.479
I'M TAKING A PICTURE AND SENDING
IT TO THE BABYSITTER.

12:26.479 --> 12:29.449
[ SIGHS ]

12:29.449 --> 12:31.251
THAT'S CUTE.

12:32.886 --> 12:36.890
I HEAR YOU'RE NOT GIVING
YOUR DAYS TO MENDOZA.

12:36.890 --> 12:40.928
I GOT TO SAVE THEM FOR NATE
AND THE CUSTODY BATTLE.

12:43.263 --> 12:44.932
I HEARD
MENDOZA GOT LIT UP

12:44.932 --> 12:46.766
'CAUSE HE WAS FUCKING
A GANGSTER'S GIRL

12:46.766 --> 12:48.468
FROM THE EASTSIDE G's.

12:48.468 --> 12:50.137
NAH. NAH.

12:50.137 --> 12:52.005
I HEARD IT
FROM A LEGIT SOURCE.

12:52.005 --> 12:54.641
EVEN IF HE SCREWED UP,

12:54.641 --> 12:56.476
DOESN'T MEAN
HE DESERVES TO GET SHOT.

12:56.476 --> 12:58.011
DON'T SHIT WHERE YOU EAT.

12:58.011 --> 13:00.647
WHEN YOU WERE LAID OUT
IN A HOSPITAL BED,

13:00.647 --> 13:02.482
DIDN'T YOU WANT EVERY
SWINGING DICK IN A BLUE SUIT

13:02.482 --> 13:04.084
OUT CHASING THE GUY
THAT SHOT YOU?

13:04.084 --> 13:05.385
THAT'S DIFFERENT.

13:05.385 --> 13:07.754
HOW?
I DIDN'T BRING THAT ON
MYSELF.

13:07.754 --> 13:10.423
YOU NEVER LIKED MENDOZA.

13:10.423 --> 13:12.425
I LIKE HIM FINE.

13:12.425 --> 13:15.328
AND I'VE KNOWN HIM
A LOT LONGER THAN YOU.

13:17.630 --> 13:18.832
DAWN, GREAT.

13:18.832 --> 13:21.401
LAST TIME, SHE THREW UP
IN THE UNIT.

13:21.401 --> 13:24.504
A36, SHOW US
ON A CITIZEN FLAG DOWN.

13:24.504 --> 13:26.073
WHAT THE HELL'S SHE DOING?

13:26.073 --> 13:27.307
I NEED SOME HELP, MAN!

13:27.307 --> 13:28.275
BACK AWAY FROM THE VEHICLE.

13:28.275 --> 13:29.209
I NEED TO TALK TO YOU,
MAN!

13:29.209 --> 13:31.845
BACK AWAY FROM THE CAR!

13:31.845 --> 13:34.781
WHAT'S GOING ON, DAWN?

13:34.781 --> 13:37.550
